    "Create your own dynamic prompts usable anywhere on your mac with keyboard shortcuts to speed up common tasks. You can reorder, delete and edit your completions.": {
      "localizations": {
        "zh-Hans": {
          "stringUnit": {
            "state": "translated",
            "value": "创建你自己的动态提示词，配合快捷键在 Mac 的任意位置使用，加速常见任务。你可以重新排序、删除和编辑这些补全。"
          }
        }
      }
    },
